<v-app-bar
  v-model="bar"
  app
  hide-on-leave="false"
>
  <v-btn
    icon
    @click="showSnackBar"
  >
    <v-icon>mdi-menu</v-icon>
  </v-btn>
  <v-btn
    icon
    @click="goBack"
  >
    <v-icon>mdi-arrow-left</v-icon>
  </v-btn>
  <v-toolbar-title
    style="cursor: pointer"
    @click="goIndex"
  >
    {{ appTitle }}
  </v-toolbar-title>
  <v-spacer />
</v-app-bar>
